To ensure safety across entire operations, EDL has defined and implemented critical safety protocols for different operational procedures including:

1. Permit to Work Safety Standard;
2. Confined Space Entry Safety Standard;
3. Lockout & Tagout Safety Standard;
4. Electrical Safety Management Standard;
5. Management of Change Standard;
6. Hot Work Safety Standard;
7. Work at Height & Façade Cradle Safety Standard;
8. Safety Observations;
9. Incident Investigation;
10.Scaffolding Safety Standard
11. Emergency Response Standard;
12. Fitout Standard;
13. Personal Protective Equipment Standard;
14. Office Safety;
15. Barricading Standard;

